[show NS]
SOUTH breaks the expected Transfer sequence by jumping to 3\H instead 
of bidding just 2\H. This is called the "Super Accept" and it shows 
a hand with four of the trump suit with maximum point count.
 

 
NORTH's \C bid and SOUTH's \D bid are Control bids, showing first 
round control of the suit that was bid.}


